wikipedia_page.main: Max McAuley Power (born 27 July 1993) is an English professional footballer who plays as a midfielder for EFL League One club Wigan Athletic. He began his career with Tranmere Rovers and then spent time with Wigan Athletic and Sunderland, making more than 100 Football League appearances with each club, before rejoining Wigan in 2021.
